:: Ocean Breeze Gwylan Juice
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<wearProp "juice" "tangerine">>
<<person1>>You bring the glass of orange juice to the balcony.
<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
	The roof of the cafe extends far enough to shield it from the <<print Weather.precipitation>>.
<</if>>
<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("met")>>
	Gwylan
<<else>>
	The mousy <<nnpc_gendery "Gwylan">>
<</if>>
seems to be lost in thought as <<he>> stares out at the ocean. You place the drink on <<his>> table.
<br><br>

"I didn't pay for that, dear," <<he>> says without looking at you. <<His>> tone is distant, but polite.
<br><br>

<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"I-it's on the house," you say. "My boss is worried about you. <<person2>><<He>> thinks you need more vitamin C."
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"I didn't ask you to pay for it," you say. "Sam is worried about you. <<person2>><<He>> thinks you're going to get scurvy."
<<else>>
	"It's on the house," you say. "My boss is worried about you, and said you need more vitamin C."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("met")>>
	<<person1>><<He>> perks up upon hearing your voice, and turns to you. "I didn't know you worked here, what a pleasant surprise!"
	<<He>> gives you a warm smile.
<<else>>
	<<person1>><<He>> sighs.
<</if>>
"I'm grateful, but I don't know what Sammy is worried about. I eat plenty of fruit," <<he>> says. "Did <<person2>><<he>> get vitamin C and vitamin D mixed up again?"
<br><br>

<<person1>><<He>> takes a small sip of the juice.
<<if !_gwylanStatus.includes("met")>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.firstMet to true>>
	After setting <<his>> drink down, <<he>> turns to you and eyes your clothes.
	<<if $worn.upper.type.includes("serving")>>
		"It's nice to see you representing Sam so well."
	<<elseif $worn.upper.type.includes("costume")>>
		"You have good taste. Not everyone would wear that while working."
	<<else>>
		"If you don't mind some advice, you may find your customers more willing to pay extra if you dress up for the job. It would help Sam out, too."
	<</if>>
	<<He>> smiles, standing up.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> looks about your age, with mousy hair and a hint of freckles. "I'm older than I look," <<he>> says, as if reading your mind.
	"<span class="green">I'm Gwylan.</span>" <<He>> reaches forward, lifts your hand, and shakes it in both <<his>> own. "Pleased to meet you. I have a shop in the outskirts of the forest. You can't miss it. I sell—"
	<<He>> pauses. "My grand<<father>> sells—" Another pause. "I sell clothes and knick-knacks there. <span class="blue">Things you won't find in normal shops.</span> Even I don't know what I have in stock!" <<He>> sounds proud.
	<br><br>

