		<br><br>

		<<He>> slowly reaches for one of your ears. <span class="red">Your arms twitch, and instinctively swat Gwylan's hand away.</span>
		<<He>> frowns. "I see. I may be able to help. <span class="blue">Come see me at the shop later, if you're not feeling like yourself.</span>"
		<<He>> leaves for the balcony.
		<<set $daily.gwylan.cafe to true>>
		<<endevent>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
	<<earSlimeCafeLinks>>
<<else>>
	당신은 try to ignore the command from the slime and continue on. You feel it try, <span class="green">but fail,</span> to force you to buy the $daily.earSlimeOceanBreezeCafeEat.
	<br><br>
	
	<<if ["cafe", "walking_to_cafe"].includes(gwylanSchedule()) and ($gwylanSeen?.includes("cafe") or $gwylan_cafe_intro) and !$gwylanSeen?.includes("ear_slime_intro")>>
		<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("ear_slime_intro")>><<set $gwylan.timer.lastSeen to Time.date.timeStamp>>
		"Are you having trouble deciding?" a familiar voice says from behind you. You turn.
		<<if !$daily.gwylan.cafe>>
			It's Gwylan, holding a plate of <<seagullFood>>.
		<<else>>
			It's Gwylan.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		"Or is it merely... <i>intrusive</i> thoughts?" <<he>> says as <<he>> walks around you.
		"Forgive me for being presumptuous, but you looked like you were struggling for a moment."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> slowly reaches for one of your ears. <span class="red">Your arms twitch, as if they were about to instinctively swat Gwylan's hand away.</span>
		<<He>> notices, and withdraws. "I may be able to help. <span class="blue">Come see me at the shop later, if you're not feeling like yourself.</span>"
		<<He>> leaves for the balcony.
		<<set $daily.gwylan.cafe to true>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	<<link [[Next|Ocean Breeze]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
